    "text": "<@U03R0B9U1GD> I agree that many accessibility issues can be solved with old and well-known tech. I think it doesn‘t happen because people don‘t look at the tech from that perspective. And for the hard-core tech people, accessibility is not a priority because there is no glory to be found there.",
