                "type": "user",
                "user_id": "U03R0B9U1GD"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": " I agree that many accessibility issues can be solved with old and well-known tech. I think it doesn‘t happen because people don‘t look at the tech from that perspective"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "."
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": " And for the hard-core tech people, accessibility is not a priority because there is no glory to be found there."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
